description:
This course is not sponsored by or affiliated with Udemy, Inc.

This course is for small businesses and entrepreneurs who want to get more FREE leads from their udemy courses.

This is not for people wanting to learn how to create a course, what to put into a course or about video editing of a course.

This is going to teach you how and why to market your udemy course and how to make udemy work for YOU!

It will teach you how to create an action plan that will help you gain student and turn those students into real leads in your business.

No more wasting time setting up courses that only make you $100

I will only be showing you the most important tactics you need to know for fast results that will have you making big money from udemy.

Extra resources will be provided when you opt-in.
title: Entrepreneurs: How to Generate Leads with Udemy - Unofficial
